name: Abhishek Ganesan
headline: Ex BlackRock | Graduate Student at SJSU
summary:
1. Collaborated with an agile team of 4 to design a microservice based architecture for Multi Asset Strategy's HAM service.      
2. Refactored the HAM monolith into 5 discrete microservices and wrote backend APIs for the same.  
3. Configured the cloud infrastructure using Spring Cloud to integrate the HAM microservices.
